race.comment: ABERLUTELY (9) was solid two back then was well bet in the latest but disappointing when midfield. Has had the tongue tie added for this and on best figures can measure right up. Worth another chance. CANDOVAL (3) is hard to assess having had one run at the picnics for the new yard. Previous form not that long ago is more than good enough for this field. Expected to do much better. DISCOBAY (7) on the other hand is in winning form, leading throughout to score with ease last time. Take catching again. DUHLATA (4) is better than last start and did win only try course and distance. Looks one of the maim hopes.
